WTF, tell me you are not one of those people that wait till full hps before you do anything. This is assuming the person doing this isnt too bright and is waiting for a set % of hps regardless of what buffs he has before he pulls.  When infact your % of hps is 100% pointless (granted there are expceptions with mob agro and stuff but not relavent here). <br>
